snippet.title: Fire Emblem Engage - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Direct 9.13.2022
snippet.description:
Become the Divine Dragon and save the continent of Elyos! Pre-order Today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/fire-emblem-engage-switch/

Use hero-summoning strategies to defeat an ancient threat in a brand-new Fire Emblem game . Summon valiant heroes like Marth & Celica alongside a new cast of characters and engage in turn-based, tactical combat against a great evil in this new Fire Emblem story.

Fire Emblem Engage launches on 1/20/23!
